       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. FINPROG.
       AUTHOR. GEMINI-CLI.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
           COPY "LOG-DATA.cpy" REPLACING LK-LOG-DATA BY WS-LOG-DATA.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
           COPY "FIN-DATA.cpy".

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING FIN-DATA.

       MAIN-LOGIC SECTION.
       000-START.
           MOVE "INFO " TO WS-LOG-LEVEL.
           MOVE "FINPROG" TO WS-LOG-SENDER.
           MOVE "CALCULATING TAX AND DISCOUNT" TO WS-LOG-MSG.
           CALL "LOGGER" USING WS-LOG-DATA.

           IF FIN-AMOUNT <= 0
               MOVE "02" TO FIN-STATUS
               MOVE "ERROR" TO WS-LOG-LEVEL
               MOVE "INVALID AMOUNT" TO WS-LOG-MSG
               CALL "LOGGER" USING WS-LOG-DATA
               GOBACK
           END-IF.

           COMPUTE FIN-TOTAL = FIN-AMOUNT + (FIN-AMOUNT * FIN-TAX-RATE).
           COMPUTE FIN-TOTAL = FIN-TOTAL - (FIN-TOTAL * FIN-DISCOUNT).

           MOVE "00" TO FIN-STATUS.
           MOVE "INFO " TO WS-LOG-LEVEL.
           MOVE "CALCULATION COMPLETED" TO WS-LOG-MSG.
           CALL "LOGGER" USING WS-LOG-DATA.

           GOBACK.
